data = lists.copy()
data.reset_index(drop=True,inplace=True)

# 简单对房子规则进行设立， house_rule
conn = []
for x in data['house_rules']:
    conn.append(len(x))

print(pd.DataFrame(conn).describe())
# IQR选择
# a['75%'] + 3*(a['75%']-a['25%'])
print(79.000000 + 3*(79.000000 - 1.000000)) # 超过313的为strict, 超过 600 --->extremely strict
# sns.distplot(conn/)
    
    
for idx,val in enumerate(conn):
    if data.ix[idx,'house_rules'] == '无':
        data.ix[idx,'house_rules'] = 'No'
        continue
        
    tmp = conn[idx]
    if  tmp > 600:
        data.ix[idx,'house_rules'] = 'extremely strict'
    elif tmp >313:
        data.ix[idx,'house_rules'] = 'strict'
    elif tmp > 50:
        data.ix[idx,'house_rules'] = 'medium strict'
    else:
        data.ix[idx,'house_rules'] = 'loose'

# 交流interaction
data = lists.copy()
data.reset_index(drop=True,inplace=True)
# 简单对interaction规则进行设立
conn = []
for x in data['interaction']:
    conn.append(len(x))

print(pd.DataFrame(conn).describe())
print(pd.DataFrame(conn).mode())
# IQR选择
# a['75%'] + 3*(a['75%']-a['25%'])
print(54.000000 + 3*(54.000000 - 1.000000)) # 超过313的为strict, 超过 600 --->extremely strict
# sns.distplot(conn)
    
    
for idx,val in enumerate(conn):
    if data.ix[idx,'interaction'] == '无':
        data.ix[idx,'interaction'] = 'No'
        continue
        
    tmp = conn[idx]
    if  tmp > 100:
        data.ix[idx,'interaction'] = 'Very enthusiastic'
    elif tmp > 50:
        data.ix[idx,'interaction'] = 'enthusiastic'
    elif tmp > 10:
        data.ix[idx,'interaction'] = 'medium enthusiastic'
    else:
        data.ix[idx,'interaction'] = 'general interaction'
